additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Not to be taken. This product is intended for use as an outdoor and indoor surface spray. Do not spray directly onto humans, pets, exposed food, water, food preparation areas or food utensils. Do not spray around fish ponds. Remove or cover fish tanks before use. Very toxic to aquatic life. Do not throw product into waterways. Very toxic to bees. Do not spray near bees. Do not spray on top of decking as surface may become slippery when wet. Formulation may cause discoloration to unsealed wood, aluminium and galvanised steel.

description: Mortein Power Gard DIY Indoor & Outdoor Surface Spray
